[rock music]

00:00:07.114 --> 00:00:14.195
♪ ♪

00:00:21.342 --> 00:00:22.344
[woman singing in Japanese]

00:00:22.344 --> 00:00:29.091
♪ ♪

00:01:39.465 --> 00:01:40.768
&gt;&gt; narrator: THIS IS THE STORY

00:01:40.768 --> 00:01:41.770
OF A MAN WHO CONTINUES TO FIGHT

00:01:41.770 --> 00:01:44.108
AGAINST DESTINY.

00:01:44.108 --> 00:01:44.843
SIMON FIGHTS, TRYING TO

00:01:44.843 --> 00:01:46.379
DISTRACT HIMSELF FROM THE HARD

00:01:46.379 --> 00:01:49.151
BLOW OF LOSING KAMINA.

00:01:49.151 --> 00:01:50.588
LAGANN GOES OUT OF CONTROL, AND

00:01:50.588 --> 00:01:52.124
WHEN IT STOPS, SIMON MEETS A

00:01:52.124 --> 00:01:53.828
MYSTERIOUS GIRL WHO APPEARS FROM

00:01:53.828 --> 00:01:56.399
OUT OF A BOX.

00:01:56.399 --> 00:01:58.169
WHEN ADIANE, THE ELEGANT, ONE OF

00:01:58.169 --> 00:01:59.606
THE SPIRAL KING’S FOUR GENERALS,

00:01:59.606 --> 00:02:01.142
ATTACKS DAI‐GURREN,

00:02:01.142 --> 00:02:03.146
THE GIRL RUNS OUT ONTO THE DECK

00:02:03.146 --> 00:02:05.652
AND SURPRISES ALL.

00:02:05.652 --> 00:02:07.321
&gt;&gt; Nia: FIRST PRINCESS NIA,

00:02:07.321 --> 00:02:08.724
DAUGHTER OF SPIRAL KING

00:02:08.724 --> 00:02:09.593
LORDGENOME!

00:02:09.593 --> 00:02:13.901
LEAVE US AT ONCE!

00:02:13.901 --> 00:02:14.870
&gt;&gt; IMPOSSIBLE!

00:02:14.870 --> 00:02:15.672
&gt;&gt; THE GIRL SAYS SHE’S PRINCESS

00:02:15.672 --> 00:02:16.740
NIA.

00:02:16.740 --> 00:02:18.143
&gt;&gt; OH, DON’T BE AN IDIOT!

00:02:18.143 --> 00:02:19.579
A PRINCESS WOULD NEVER LEAVE THE

00:02:19.579 --> 00:02:20.581
CAPITAL AND GO WANDERING AROUND

00:02:20.581 --> 00:02:21.717
OUTSIDE!

00:02:21.717 --> 00:02:23.654
&gt;&gt; BUT, MA’AM, SHE LOOKS EXACTLY

00:02:23.654 --> 00:02:25.825
LIKE THE PRINCESS.

00:02:25.825 --> 00:02:27.161
&gt;&gt; YOU THINK SO?

00:02:27.161 --> 00:02:28.229
WELL, IN THAT CASE, WE’LL JUST

00:02:28.229 --> 00:02:29.231
HAVE TO KILL HER AND PRETEND WE

00:02:29.231 --> 00:02:30.133
NEVER SAW HER!

00:02:30.133 --> 00:02:31.503
&gt;&gt; GENERAL ADIANE, PLEASE!

00:02:31.503 --> 00:02:34.241
WATCH WHAT YOU SAY!

00:02:34.241 --> 00:02:35.410
ALL OUR TRANSMISSIONS ARE

00:02:35.410 --> 00:02:37.147
BEING RECORDED!

00:02:40.722 --> 00:02:42.458
&gt;&gt; LOOK, HER BACK IS TURNED!

00:02:42.458 --> 00:02:43.326
&gt;&gt; Ron: DID OUR LITTLE PRINCESS

00:02:43.326 --> 00:02:44.896
REALLY STOP HER FROM ATTACKING?

00:02:44.896 --> 00:02:46.767
&gt;&gt; FIRE CANNON!

00:02:46.767 --> 00:02:47.702
FIRE, FIRE, FIRE!

00:02:47.702 --> 00:02:48.504
&gt;&gt; Ron: DIDN’T YOU LISTEN?

00:02:48.504 --> 00:02:50.140
THE CANNONS ARE OFFLINE.

00:02:50.140 --> 00:02:51.142
&gt;&gt; LET’S GET ONE THING STRAIGHT,

00:02:51.142 --> 00:02:52.244
YOU STINKING HUMANS!

00:02:52.244 --> 00:02:53.380
I AM NOT RETREATING!

00:02:53.380 --> 00:02:55.283
I’LL BE BACK, GOT IT?

00:02:55.283 --> 00:02:58.189
[Team Dai‐Gurren jeering]

00:03:03.501 --> 00:03:06.907
&gt;&gt; Simon: WHAT IS A "PRINCESS"?

00:03:06.907 --> 00:03:08.476
&gt;&gt; Yoko: IT’S WHAT YOU CALL THE

00:03:08.476 --> 00:03:10.280
DAUGHTER OF A KING.

00:03:10.280 --> 00:03:11.683
&gt;&gt; MAN, THIS IS UNBELIEVABLE.

00:03:11.683 --> 00:03:13.286
HE BROUGHT THE DAUGHTER OF THE

00:03:13.286 --> 00:03:16.492
GUY WE’RE FIGHTING ONBOARD.

00:03:16.492 --> 00:03:18.697
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: SHOULD WE HOLD HER?

00:03:18.697 --> 00:03:20.200
&gt;&gt; SO WHAT’S THE PLAN, KITTAN?

00:03:20.200 --> 00:03:21.269
&gt;&gt; THE PLAN?

00:03:21.269 --> 00:03:22.204
&gt;&gt; TELL US THE PLAN!

00:03:22.204 --> 00:03:23.674
TELL US THE PLAN!

00:03:23.674 --> 00:03:24.676
&gt;&gt; Kittan: WHATEVER THE CASE, WE

00:03:24.676 --> 00:03:25.945
INTERROGATE HER IN THE MORNING.

00:03:25.945 --> 00:03:27.347
I AM GONNA PUT THE SCREWS TO

00:03:27.347 --> 00:03:28.651
THAT LITTLE GIRL AND MAKE HER

00:03:28.651 --> 00:03:30.187
SPILL EVERYTHING SHE KNOWS!

00:03:36.667 --> 00:03:37.969
&gt;&gt; ADIANE, THE ELEGANT FLED IN

00:03:37.969 --> 00:03:40.842
THE FACE OF THE ENEMY?

00:03:40.842 --> 00:03:42.545
WHAT MANNER OF JOKE IS THIS

00:03:42.545 --> 00:03:43.581
SUPPOSED TO BE?

00:03:43.581 --> 00:03:45.918
&gt;&gt; SIRE, OUR DASTARDLY ENEMIES,

00:03:45.918 --> 00:03:47.454
THOSE PATHETIC HUMANS, WERE

00:03:47.454 --> 00:03:49.593
HOLDING PRINCESS NIA HOSTAGE.

00:03:49.593 --> 00:03:51.262
&gt;&gt; YOU FOOL.

00:03:51.262 --> 00:03:54.268
I HAVE LONG SINCE CAST THAT GIRL

00:03:54.268 --> 00:03:55.705
OUT.

00:03:55.705 --> 00:03:56.840
I DON’T CARE WHAT HAPPENS TO

00:03:56.840 --> 00:03:57.742
HER.

00:03:57.742 --> 00:03:58.944
&gt;&gt; YOU CAST HER OUT?

00:03:58.944 --> 00:04:01.382
BUT, SIRE, I HAD NO WAY OF

00:04:01.382 --> 00:04:02.317
KNOWING THAT DURING MY

00:04:02.317 --> 00:04:03.754
CONFRONTATION, SINCE I WAS NEVER

00:04:03.754 --> 00:04:04.756
INFORMED OF THIS.

00:04:04.756 --> 00:04:07.294
&gt;&gt; YOU DARE USE YOUR LACK OF

00:04:07.294 --> 00:04:08.931
KNOWLEDGE TO EXCUSE YOUR

00:04:08.931 --> 00:04:09.833
FAILURE?

00:04:09.833 --> 00:04:10.768
&gt;&gt; NO, SIRE.

00:04:10.768 --> 00:04:11.670
&gt;&gt; YOU COMMITTED THE GRAVE

00:04:11.670 --> 00:04:13.239
OFFENSE OF FLEEING IN THE FACE

00:04:13.239 --> 00:04:15.812
OF THE ENEMY, JUST TO PROTECT

00:04:15.812 --> 00:04:17.448
A GIRL WHO IS NO LONGER

00:04:17.448 --> 00:04:18.349
A PRINCESS.

00:04:18.349 --> 00:04:20.655
OH, THE ABSURDITY OF IT ALL.

00:04:20.655 --> 00:04:23.026
[laughing]

00:04:23.026 --> 00:04:24.930
&gt;&gt; SIRE, PLEASE, YOU MUST GIVE

00:04:24.930 --> 00:04:26.700
ME, ADIANE, THE ELEGANT,

00:04:26.700 --> 00:04:27.502
ANOTHER CHANCE.

00:04:27.502 --> 00:04:29.940
&gt;&gt; OH? YOU DARE TELL ME WHAT I

00:04:29.940 --> 00:04:31.008
MUST DO?

00:04:31.008 --> 00:04:31.810
&gt;&gt; I WOULD NOT DREAM OF IT,

00:04:31.810 --> 00:04:32.545
SIRE!

00:04:32.545 --> 00:04:33.948
&gt;&gt; WHAT IS IT, THEN?

00:04:33.948 --> 00:04:36.486
&gt;&gt; MAJESTY, TO PROVE MY LOYALTY,

00:04:36.486 --> 00:04:37.655
I SHALL SET OUT ALONE

00:04:37.655 --> 00:04:38.557
IN SAYRUNE.

00:04:38.557 --> 00:04:39.993
I SHALL WIPE OUT THE HUMANS AND

00:04:39.993 --> 00:04:42.565
DAI‐GUNZAN, AND I SHALL KILL NIA

00:04:42.565 --> 00:04:43.634
ALONG WITH THEM.

00:04:43.634 --> 00:04:45.003
I WILL DO ALL OF THIS BEFORE

00:04:45.003 --> 00:04:46.038
SUNSET TOMORROW.

00:04:46.038 --> 00:04:48.611
&gt;&gt; VERY WELL, BUT BEAR IN MIND

00:04:48.611 --> 00:04:49.613
YOU WILL NOT RECEIVE

00:04:49.613 --> 00:04:50.982
ANOTHER CHANCE.

00:04:50.982 --> 00:04:52.585
NOW GO.

00:04:52.585 --> 00:04:55.558
[footsteps]

00:04:55.558 --> 00:04:56.560
&gt;&gt; GENERAL ADIANE.

00:04:56.560 --> 00:04:57.461
&gt;&gt; VIRAL?

00:04:57.461 --> 00:04:58.697
I THOUGHT YOU WERE BADLY

00:04:58.697 --> 00:04:59.365
INJURED.

00:04:59.365 --> 00:05:00.735
&gt;&gt; NO, MA’AM. I’LL BE RETURNING

00:05:00.735 --> 00:05:01.937
TO MY HOME UNIT TOMORROW.

00:05:01.937 --> 00:05:03.306
FAILING TO PROTECT GENERAL

00:05:03.306 --> 00:05:04.776
THYMILPH IS THE GREATEST

00:05:04.776 --> 00:05:06.847
DEFEAT OF MY LIFE.

00:05:06.847 --> 00:05:08.383
THAT SAID, I WOULD VERY MUCH

00:05:08.383 --> 00:05:09.886
LIKE TO ASK A FAVOR OF‐‐

00:05:13.861 --> 00:05:14.930
GENERAL ADIANE.

00:05:14.930 --> 00:05:16.365
&gt;&gt; GO ON, VIRAL.

00:05:16.365 --> 00:05:18.303
I WILL HEAR YOU OUT.

00:05:18.303 --> 00:05:20.575
&gt;&gt; DURING YOUR NEXT MISSION, I‐‐

00:05:20.575 --> 00:05:22.311
ASK THAT YOU‐‐

00:05:22.311 --> 00:05:23.647
ALLOW ME‐‐

00:05:23.647 --> 00:05:25.417
ALLOW ME TO‐‐

00:05:25.417 --> 00:05:27.522
TO ACCOMPANY‐‐

00:05:27.522 --> 00:05:29.325
ACCOMPANY YOU.

00:05:29.325 --> 00:05:31.095
&gt;&gt; I HAD THYMILPH IN MY DEBT,

00:05:31.095 --> 00:05:32.431
RIGHT WHERE I WANTED HIM TO BE.

00:05:32.431 --> 00:05:33.466
BUT NOW THAT HE’S DEAD, MY

00:05:33.466 --> 00:05:34.335
SCHEMING TURNS OUT TO BE FOR

00:05:34.335 --> 00:05:35.403
NOTHING!

00:05:35.403 --> 00:05:36.305
AND IT’S ALL BECAUSE YOU’RE A

00:05:36.305 --> 00:05:37.775
WORTHLESS, INCOMPETENT MORON!

00:05:37.775 --> 00:05:39.378
&gt;&gt; WHICH IS WHY I BEG THAT YOU

00:05:39.378 --> 00:05:40.715
GIVE ME A CHANCE TO AVENGE HIS

00:05:40.715 --> 00:05:41.683
DEATH.

00:05:41.683 --> 00:05:42.719
&gt;&gt; I’VE ALREADY DECIDED I’LL BE

00:05:42.719 --> 00:05:44.523
GOING OUT ALONE TOMORROW

00:05:44.523 --> 00:05:45.390
MORNING.

00:05:45.390 --> 00:05:47.629
GO BACK TO YOUR DEN.

00:05:47.629 --> 00:05:49.064
I WILL BE THE ONE AVENGING

00:05:49.064 --> 00:05:52.605
THYMILPH, NO ONE ELSE.

00:05:56.078 --> 00:05:56.947
&gt;&gt; SHOVE EVERY USABLE

00:05:56.947 --> 00:05:58.349
PART OUTSIDE!

00:05:58.349 --> 00:05:59.418
WE CAN’T DO ANY WORK WITH THIS

00:05:59.418 --> 00:06:00.487
JUNK IN THE WAY!

00:06:00.487 --> 00:06:03.661
[team chattering]

00:06:03.661 --> 00:06:05.363
&gt;&gt; Nia: THANK YOU FOR THE FOOD.

00:06:05.363 --> 00:06:06.365
&gt;&gt; THANK YOU FOR THE FO‐O‐OD!

00:06:06.365 --> 00:06:07.702
&gt;&gt; THANK YOU FOR THE FOOD!

00:06:07.702 --> 00:06:09.806
&gt;&gt; YUMMY!

00:06:09.806 --> 00:06:11.108
WHAT’S THIS STUFF?

00:06:11.108 --> 00:06:13.747
IT LOOKS GREAT!

00:06:13.747 --> 00:06:14.783
&gt;&gt; I CAN’T CUT MINE.

00:06:14.783 --> 00:06:16.553
&gt;&gt; Nia: JUST A MOMENT.

00:06:16.553 --> 00:06:18.524
I’LL CUT IT FOR YOU.

00:06:18.524 --> 00:06:19.893
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: SO, ANYWAY, UH...

00:06:19.893 --> 00:06:22.030
WELL, UH, PRINCESS, I...

00:06:22.030 --> 00:06:23.934
&gt;&gt; WHAT IS IT?

00:06:23.934 --> 00:06:24.903
WOULD YOU LIKE SOME TOO?

00:06:24.903 --> 00:06:29.478
OPEN WIDE!

00:06:29.478 --> 00:06:30.815
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: HEY, THAT’S GOOD.

00:06:30.815 --> 00:06:32.417
WOW, GRAMPS, YOU’RE A PRETTY

00:06:32.417 --> 00:06:33.587
INCREDIBLE COOK.

00:06:33.587 --> 00:06:34.421
&gt;&gt; IS HE REALLY?

00:06:34.421 --> 00:06:36.793
&gt;&gt; YOU SERIOUS?

00:06:36.793 --> 00:06:37.629
&gt;&gt; Kittan: WHAT ARE YOU GUYS,

00:06:37.629 --> 00:06:38.429
MORONS?!

00:06:38.429 --> 00:06:39.899
WHAT ARE YOU DOING THROWING THIS

00:06:39.899 --> 00:06:41.536
GIRL A NICE FRIENDLY DINNER?

00:06:41.536 --> 00:06:42.572
YOU DON’T HAVE TO ROLL OUT THE

00:06:42.572 --> 00:06:43.874
RED CARPET FOR HER!

00:06:43.874 --> 00:06:44.876
WE’RE HERE TO CONDUCT AN

00:06:44.876 --> 00:06:45.878
INTERROGATION!

00:06:45.878 --> 00:06:47.649
YOU’D BETTER TALK!

00:06:47.649 --> 00:06:49.451
[Nia giggles]

00:06:49.451 --> 00:06:50.554
&gt;&gt; Nia: HOW DO YOU DO, SIR?

00:06:50.554 --> 00:06:51.389
IT IS LOVELY TO MEET YOU.

00:06:51.389 --> 00:06:52.825
I’M NIA.

00:06:52.825 --> 00:06:56.165
NOW THEN, WHAT’S YOUR NAME?

00:06:56.165 --> 00:06:58.169
&gt;&gt; Kittan: MY NAME IS KITTAN!

00:06:58.169 --> 00:06:59.873
I’M THE ELDEST OF THE BLACK

00:06:59.873 --> 00:07:00.975
SIBLINGS, AND NOT ONLY THAT,

00:07:00.975 --> 00:07:02.679
I’M THE LEADER OF TEAM GURREN,

00:07:02.679 --> 00:07:03.479
THAT’S WHO I AM!

00:07:03.479 --> 00:07:05.551
&gt;&gt; Nia: KITTAN, YOU SAY?

00:07:05.551 --> 00:07:07.522
IT’S A PLEASURE.

00:07:07.522 --> 00:07:08.824
&gt;&gt; Kittan: ALL RIGHT, LOOK, JUST

00:07:08.824 --> 00:07:09.859
BECAUSE YOU’RE SWEET AND CUTE

00:07:09.859 --> 00:07:11.095
AND NICE AND ALL DOESN’T CHANGE

00:07:11.095 --> 00:07:12.497
THE FACT THAT YOU’RE THE ENEMY!

00:07:12.497 --> 00:07:13.199
&gt;&gt; SHE ENEMY!

00:07:13.199 --> 00:07:14.435
&gt;&gt; HE’S RIGHT!

00:07:14.435 --> 00:07:15.938
&gt;&gt; both: LITTLE GIRL ENEMY!

00:07:15.938 --> 00:07:16.873
&gt;&gt; Nia: TELL ME, KITTAN?

00:07:16.873 --> 00:07:20.715
WHAT DOES "ENEMY" MEAN?

00:07:20.715 --> 00:07:21.783
&gt;&gt; Kittan: AN ENEMY IS A BAD

00:07:21.783 --> 00:07:22.685
PERSON!

00:07:22.685 --> 00:07:23.721
SOMEONE YOU JUST GOTTA BEAT THE

00:07:23.721 --> 00:07:25.090
CRAP OUT OF!

00:07:25.090 --> 00:07:26.025
&gt;&gt; Nia: "BEAT THE CRAP OUT OF"?

00:07:26.025 --> 00:07:27.829
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

00:07:27.829 --> 00:07:29.933
&gt;&gt; Kittan: WELL, UH, IT’S WHEN

00:07:29.933 --> 00:07:31.703
YOU TAKE YOUR FIST AND YOU BELT

00:07:31.703 --> 00:07:32.137
THE OTHER GUY, AND‐‐

00:07:32.137 --> 00:07:33.774
&gt;&gt; Nia: WHAT DOES "FIST" MEAN?

00:07:33.774 --> 00:07:35.544
&gt;&gt; Kittan: WELL, OKAY, LOOK,

00:07:35.544 --> 00:07:36.012
A FIST IS‐‐

00:07:36.012 --> 00:07:36.913
&gt;&gt; Nia: WHY WOULD YOU DO THAT

00:07:36.913 --> 00:07:37.481
TO SOMEBODY?

00:07:37.481 --> 00:07:39.084
&gt;&gt; Kittan: BECAUSE THAT SOMEBODY

00:07:39.084 --> 00:07:39.753
PISSED ME OFF!

00:07:39.753 --> 00:07:40.955
&gt;&gt; Nia: WHAT DOES IT MEAN TO BE

00:07:40.955 --> 00:07:41.757
"PISSED OFF"?

00:07:41.757 --> 00:07:43.092
&gt;&gt; HE’S SUPPOSED TO INTERROGATE

00:07:43.092 --> 00:07:43.694
HER...

00:07:43.694 --> 00:07:44.696
&gt;&gt; BUT SHE’S INTERROGATING HIM

00:07:44.696 --> 00:07:45.463
INSTEAD.

00:07:45.463 --> 00:07:47.467
&gt;&gt; YOU KNOW, OUR BRO WAS NEVER

00:07:47.467 --> 00:07:48.570
TOO GOOD AROUND HER TYPE.

00:07:48.570 --> 00:07:49.973
&gt;&gt; Kittan: HEY, BUTT OUT!

00:07:49.973 --> 00:07:50.975
&gt;&gt; Nia: KITTAN, YOU ARE...

00:07:50.975 --> 00:07:52.979
YOU ARE A‐‐LET’S SEE.

00:07:52.979 --> 00:07:54.716
YOU’RE A "NOT‐PISSING‐OFF

00:07:54.716 --> 00:07:56.118
PERSON," AND YOU’RE SWEET.

00:07:56.118 --> 00:07:57.087
I THANK YOU!

00:07:57.087 --> 00:07:59.058
OUR TALK HAS BEEN INFORMATIVE!

00:07:59.058 --> 00:08:01.530
&gt;&gt; Kittan: WELL, NO PROBLEM!

00:08:01.530 --> 00:08:02.565
I’M THE LEADER HERE, SO IT’S

00:08:02.565 --> 00:08:04.468
ONLY NATURAL.

00:08:04.468 --> 00:08:07.107
[murmuring from crowd]

00:08:16.492 --> 00:08:17.695
&gt;&gt; Kittan: NOW LISTEN UP.

00:08:17.695 --> 00:08:19.866
AS TEAM LEADER, I GOT AN ORDER

00:08:19.866 --> 00:08:20.601
FOR YOU.

00:08:20.601 --> 00:08:22.037
I WANT YOU TO GET ALL THE ENEMY

00:08:22.037 --> 00:08:23.473
INTEL YOU CAN OUT OF HER.

00:08:23.473 --> 00:08:24.909
&gt;&gt; Simon: WHY ME?

00:08:24.909 --> 00:08:25.811
&gt;&gt; Kittan: COME ON.

00:08:25.811 --> 00:08:26.713
JUST DO IT, SIMON.

00:08:26.713 --> 00:08:27.849
YOU’RE THE ONE WHO BROUGHT

00:08:27.849 --> 00:08:28.216
HER HERE.

00:08:28.216 --> 00:08:29.051
SHE’S HERE BECAUSE OF YOU.

00:08:29.051 --> 00:08:30.521
MAN UP AND FIX IT.

00:08:30.521 --> 00:08:31.890
SHE’S A FORMIDABLE OPPONENT.

00:08:31.890 --> 00:08:33.059
KNOW THAT YOU’RE IN FOR A TOUGH

00:08:33.059 --> 00:08:36.499
FIGHT.

00:08:36.499 --> 00:08:37.602
&gt;&gt; Nia: I HEARD MANY THINGS FROM

00:08:37.602 --> 00:08:39.104
KITTAN.

00:08:39.104 --> 00:08:40.808
HE SAID MY FATHER IS DOING

00:08:40.808 --> 00:08:42.077
TERRIBLE THINGS TO PEOPLE

00:08:42.077 --> 00:08:42.879
ON THE SURFACE.

00:08:42.879 --> 00:08:45.083
IT’S HARD TO IMAGINE THAT FATHER

00:08:45.083 --> 00:08:46.686
WOULD DO SUCH THINGS WITHOUT

00:08:46.686 --> 00:08:47.287
GOOD REASON.

00:08:47.287 --> 00:08:49.692
AND YET, I DO NOT BELIEVE THAT

00:08:49.692 --> 00:08:51.530
THE PEOPLE HERE ARE BAD.

00:08:51.530 --> 00:08:52.230
&gt;&gt; Simon: WE DIDN’T DO ANYTHING

00:08:52.230 --> 00:08:53.700
WRONG, NIA.

00:08:53.700 --> 00:08:54.836
IT’S THE SPIRAL KING WHO’S THE

00:08:54.836 --> 00:08:56.506
BAD GUY HERE,

00:08:56.506 --> 00:08:57.709
HIM AND HIS PEOPLE.

00:08:57.709 --> 00:08:59.612
&gt;&gt; Nia: DO YOU HATE MY FATHER?

00:08:59.612 --> 00:09:01.115
&gt;&gt; Simon: OF COURSE I DO.

00:09:01.115 --> 00:09:03.620
&gt;&gt; Nia: DO YOU ALSO HATE ME?

00:09:03.620 --> 00:09:04.556
&gt;&gt; Simon: I DON’T KNOW WHAT TO

00:09:04.556 --> 00:09:05.691
SAY TO THAT.

00:09:05.691 --> 00:09:06.626
&gt;&gt; Nia: SO THEN, WHY IS IT THAT

00:09:06.626 --> 00:09:08.096
YOU FIGHT?

00:09:08.096 --> 00:09:09.966
&gt;&gt; Simon: IT WAS MY BRO WHO GAVE

00:09:09.966 --> 00:09:10.935
ME THE STRENGTH TO FIGHT.

00:09:10.935 --> 00:09:13.172
I FOUGHT BECAUSE HE

00:09:13.172 --> 00:09:15.310
BELIEVED IN ME.

00:09:15.310 --> 00:09:18.015
Nia: SIMON.

00:09:18.015 --> 00:09:21.122
TELL ME, WHO IS THIS BRO PERSON?

00:09:21.122 --> 00:09:23.292
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: SO DO YOU THINK

00:09:23.292 --> 00:09:24.696
SIMON WILL BE ALL RIGHT?

00:09:24.696 --> 00:09:25.831
&gt;&gt; Ron: DON’T YOU HAVE OTHER

00:09:25.831 --> 00:09:27.602
THINGS TO WORRY ABOUT?

00:09:27.602 --> 00:09:28.737
IF I DON’T FINALLY GET

00:09:28.737 --> 00:09:30.106
DAI‐GURREN HERE RUNNING AGAIN,

00:09:30.106 --> 00:09:31.308
A LOT MORE THAN TEARS WILL BE

00:09:31.308 --> 00:09:33.680
SPILLED.

00:09:33.680 --> 00:09:35.016
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: YES, I SUPPOSE,

00:09:35.016 --> 00:09:36.653
BUT IN SIMON’S CASE....

00:09:36.653 --> 00:09:38.557
&gt;&gt; Ron: LOOK, WE’RE ALL FIGHTING

00:09:38.557 --> 00:09:39.124
HERE, AREN’T WE?

00:09:39.124 --> 00:09:40.761
AND THAT GOES FOR YOU, TOO?

00:09:40.761 --> 00:09:42.164
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: YES, BUT...

00:09:42.164 --> 00:09:44.067
&gt;&gt; Ron: BESIDES, IF THE REASON

00:09:44.067 --> 00:09:45.336
THAT LAGANN ISN’T WORKING IS

00:09:45.336 --> 00:09:46.338
BECAUSE IT DOESN’T FEEL LIKE

00:09:46.338 --> 00:09:47.708
HELPING A KID WHO’S LOST THE

00:09:47.708 --> 00:09:48.744
WILL TO SURVIVE...

00:09:48.744 --> 00:09:52.752
I THINK IT HAS THE RIGHT IDEA.

00:09:52.752 --> 00:09:54.221
&gt;&gt; Nia: OH, HOW SAD.

00:09:54.221 --> 00:09:56.258
SO HE WAS KILLED IN A BATTLE.

00:09:56.258 --> 00:09:57.695
&gt;&gt; Simon: THAT’S RIGHT.

00:09:57.695 --> 00:09:58.664
&gt;&gt; Nia: THEN I SUPPOSE IT’S

00:09:58.664 --> 00:10:00.333
LITTLE WONDER THAT EVERYONE HERE

00:10:00.333 --> 00:10:01.235
HATES ME.

00:10:01.235 --> 00:10:02.738
I REALLY CAN’T BLAME THEM.

00:10:02.738 --> 00:10:04.108
&gt;&gt; Simon: DON’T YOU WORRY ABOUT

00:10:04.108 --> 00:10:04.809
THAT, NIA.

00:10:04.809 --> 00:10:06.345
NOBODY HERE HATES YOU.

00:10:06.345 --> 00:10:08.216
ACTUALLY, I DON’T THINK THAT

00:10:08.216 --> 00:10:10.855
BRO EVER FOUGHT OUT OF HATRED.

00:10:10.855 --> 00:10:13.359
IT’S HARD TO EXPLAIN, BUT NO

00:10:13.359 --> 00:10:15.230
MATTER HOW BAD THE SITUATION,

00:10:15.230 --> 00:10:17.200
HE WAS ALWAYS LAUGHING.

00:10:17.200 --> 00:10:19.739
I GUESS, IN A WAY, HE WAS...

00:10:19.739 --> 00:10:20.708
&gt;&gt; Yoko: A MAN OF UNLIMITED

00:10:20.708 --> 00:10:24.782
STUPIDITY!

00:10:24.782 --> 00:10:25.985
I’D LIKE TO HEAR ABOUT HIM,

00:10:25.985 --> 00:10:26.786
TOO, SIMON.

00:10:26.786 --> 00:10:28.222
PLEASE KEEP GOING.

00:10:28.222 --> 00:10:29.626
&gt;&gt; Simon: THIS HAPPENED A LONG

00:10:29.626 --> 00:10:30.794
TIME BEFORE WE MET YOU.

00:10:30.794 --> 00:10:32.698
IT WAS BRO’S IDEA TO BREAK OUT

00:10:32.698 --> 00:10:33.967
FROM OUR UNDERGROUND VILLAGE AND

00:10:33.967 --> 00:10:34.903
THEN DIG OUR WAY UP

00:10:34.903 --> 00:10:35.771
TO THE SURFACE.

00:10:35.771 --> 00:10:37.340
BUT ALONG THE WAY, THE TUNNELS

00:10:37.340 --> 00:10:38.610
COLLAPSED BECAUSE OF AN

00:10:38.610 --> 00:10:39.278
EARTHQUAKE, AND WE WERE

00:10:39.278 --> 00:10:40.280
ALL TRAPPED.

00:10:40.280 --> 00:10:43.720
&gt;&gt; Yoko: HEY, THIS STORY IS...

00:10:43.720 --> 00:10:45.356
NEVER MIND.

00:10:45.356 --> 00:10:46.960
&gt;&gt; Simon: IT WAS SCARY.

00:10:46.960 --> 00:10:48.362
I WAS TERRIFIED THAT I

00:10:48.362 --> 00:10:49.766
WAS GOING TO BE BURIED ALIVE

00:10:49.766 --> 00:10:52.103
JUST LIKE MY MOM AND DAD WERE.

00:10:52.103 --> 00:10:54.642
BUT BRO URGED US ON, YELLING,

00:10:54.642 --> 00:10:56.947
"COME ON, ONWARDS AND UPWARDS,

00:10:56.947 --> 00:10:57.715
MEN..."

00:10:57.715 --> 00:11:00.286
LAUGHING THE WHOLE TIME.

00:11:00.286 --> 00:11:02.290
MY HANDS FINALLY STOPPED

00:11:02.290 --> 00:11:03.392
SHAKING.

00:11:03.392 --> 00:11:05.096
WHEN I’M FOCUSED ON DRILLING, I

00:11:05.096 --> 00:11:06.833
CAN HEAR THE SOIL AND THE ROCKS

00:11:06.833 --> 00:11:07.300
CALLING TO ME.

00:11:07.300 --> 00:11:09.304
"IT’S SOFTER THIS WAY," OR

00:11:09.304 --> 00:11:10.641
"TRY DIGGING OVER HERE!"

00:11:10.641 --> 00:11:13.981
I FOLLOW THEIR ADVICE AS I DIG.

00:11:13.981 --> 00:11:16.085
IF WE HAD ALLOWED OURSELVES TO

00:11:16.085 --> 00:11:17.254
JUST GIVE UP THAT DAY,

00:11:17.254 --> 00:11:19.659
THEN WE ALL WOULD HAVE DIED.

00:11:19.659 --> 00:11:21.095
THE ONLY REASON WE DIDN’T GIVE

00:11:21.095 --> 00:11:22.698
UP WAS ’CAUSE BRO WAS WITH US.

00:11:22.698 --> 00:11:24.434
AND HE DIDN’T GIVE UP.

00:11:24.434 --> 00:11:26.272
HE REFUSED.

00:11:26.272 --> 00:11:28.075
THAT’S HOW HE ALWAYS WAS.

00:11:28.075 --> 00:11:30.346
WITHOUT HIM, I CAN’T DO

00:11:30.346 --> 00:11:32.685
ANYTHING.

00:11:32.685 --> 00:11:34.789
THAT’S WHY I HAVE TO DO WHAT I

00:11:34.789 --> 00:11:36.893
CAN TO BECOME LIKE HIM, SO I

00:11:36.893 --> 00:11:38.931
CAN DO HIS SHARE FOR HIM.

00:11:38.931 --> 00:11:41.035
&gt;&gt; Nia: THAT’S NOT TRUE.

00:11:41.035 --> 00:11:43.039
YOU RESCUED ME FROM THAT AWFUL

00:11:43.039 --> 00:11:44.107
GUNMEN ALL BY YOURSELF,

00:11:44.107 --> 00:11:44.909
REMEMBER?

00:11:44.909 --> 00:11:45.878
&gt;&gt; Simon: BUT THAT WASN’T...

00:11:45.878 --> 00:11:47.180
&gt;&gt; Nia: I BELIEVE YOU CAN DO

00:11:47.180 --> 00:11:48.249
FINE ON YOUR OWN.

00:11:48.249 --> 00:11:49.953
WHY DO YOU SPEND SO MUCH TIME

00:11:49.953 --> 00:11:51.823
OBSESSING OVER THIS BRO PERSON?

00:11:51.823 --> 00:11:53.159
&gt;&gt; Simon: WHY?

00:11:53.159 --> 00:11:55.196
YOU’RE JUST... SAYING THIS

00:11:55.196 --> 00:11:56.933
BECAUSE YOU DIDN’T KNOW HIM.

00:11:56.933 --> 00:11:58.336
&gt;&gt; Nia: I CANNOT GET TO KNOW

00:11:58.336 --> 00:12:00.106
SOMEONE WHO ISN’T HERE.

00:12:00.106 --> 00:12:02.912
BUT ALSO YOU CANNOT RELY ON

00:12:02.912 --> 00:12:04.281
SOMEONE WHO ISN’T HERE.

00:12:04.281 --> 00:12:05.149
&gt;&gt; Simon: NIA!

00:12:05.149 --> 00:12:06.051
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YOU CAN’T POSSIBLY HAVE

00:12:06.051 --> 00:12:08.222
ANY IDEA HOW SIMON IS FEELING!

00:12:08.222 --> 00:12:09.224
YOU CAN’T, ’CAUSE YOU DIDN’T

00:12:09.224 --> 00:12:10.928
KNOW KAMINA!

00:12:10.928 --> 00:12:12.130
&gt;&gt; Nia: I MAY NOT HAVE KNOWN

00:12:12.130 --> 00:12:13.332
THIS BRO PERSON, BUT I

00:12:13.332 --> 00:12:14.368
UNDERSTAND SIMON.

00:12:14.368 --> 00:12:16.372
HE IS NOT A HELPLESS PERSON.

00:12:16.372 --> 00:12:17.909
BUT IF HE KEEPS DWELLING ON THE

00:12:17.909 --> 00:12:19.411
MEMORY OF SOMEONE WHO’S GONE,

00:12:19.411 --> 00:12:20.213
THEN...

00:12:20.213 --> 00:12:21.783
&gt;&gt; Yoko: YOU LITTLE...

00:12:21.783 --> 00:12:22.885
DON’T TALK LIKE YOU’RE

00:12:22.885 --> 00:12:24.288
SOME INNOCENT BYSTANDER.

00:12:24.288 --> 00:12:25.758
YOU KNOW PERFECTLY WELL WHOSE

00:12:25.758 --> 00:12:27.394
FAULT IT IS THAT KAMINA’S DEAD!

00:12:27.394 --> 00:12:29.298
SO DON’T YOU DARE STAND THERE

00:12:29.298 --> 00:12:33.941
AND CALMLY LECTURE SIMON.

00:12:33.941 --> 00:12:38.316
&gt;&gt; Nia: I APOLOGIZE.

00:12:38.316 --> 00:12:40.486
&gt;&gt; Yoko: WHAT YOU SAID IS RIGHT.

00:12:40.486 --> 00:12:42.223
NO AMOUNT OF CRYING OR GRIEVING

00:12:42.223 --> 00:12:43.459
WILL BRING KAMINA BACK.

00:12:43.459 --> 00:12:45.496
WE’RE WELL AWARE OF THAT.

00:12:45.496 --> 00:12:47.367
MAYBE IT WOULD BE EASIER IF WE

00:12:47.367 --> 00:12:49.237
COULD FORGET ABOUT HIM.

00:12:49.237 --> 00:12:50.908
BUT WE CAN’T JUST...

00:12:50.908 --> 00:12:53.012
WE CAN’T JUST...

00:12:53.012 --> 00:12:54.314
WE CAN’T FORGET ABOUT HIM LIKE

00:12:54.314 --> 00:12:56.118
HE WAS NOTHING!

00:13:09.478 --> 00:13:11.248
&gt;&gt; Nia: SHE HAD TEARS IN HER

00:13:11.248 --> 00:13:12.350
EYES.

00:13:12.350 --> 00:13:13.854
&gt;&gt; Simon: IT ISN’T YOUR FAULT,

00:13:13.854 --> 00:13:14.889
NIA.

00:13:14.889 --> 00:13:16.993
&gt;&gt; Nia: I WANT SO VERY MUCH TO

00:13:16.993 --> 00:13:18.864
LEARN ABOUT YOUR PEOPLE.

00:13:39.539 --> 00:13:42.344
&gt;&gt; WH‐‐WHAT IN THE HELL IS THAT?

00:13:42.344 --> 00:13:43.379
WE GOT TROUBLE!

00:13:43.379 --> 00:13:44.448
A WALL OF WATER IS COMING

00:13:44.448 --> 00:13:45.116
THIS WAY!

00:13:45.116 --> 00:13:45.918
&gt;&gt; WATER?

00:13:45.918 --> 00:13:47.153
&gt;&gt; MAYBE HE’S SEEING THINGS

00:13:47.153 --> 00:13:48.356
AFTER BEING COOPED UP‐‐

00:13:57.240 --> 00:14:01.415
&gt;&gt; ENEMY GUNMEN ON OUR DECK!

00:14:01.415 --> 00:14:03.419
&gt;&gt; I’VE RETURNED, JUST AS I

00:14:03.419 --> 00:14:04.354
PROMISED I WOULD.

00:14:04.354 --> 00:14:05.524
STINKING HUMANS!

00:14:05.524 --> 00:14:07.060
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: WHAT THE HELL WAS

00:14:07.060 --> 00:14:07.595
THAT ALL A‐‐

00:14:07.595 --> 00:14:08.597
&gt;&gt; Kittan: HEY, IT’S THAT CHICK

00:14:08.597 --> 00:14:09.297
WITH THE FINS!

00:14:09.297 --> 00:14:10.901
&gt;&gt; FIRST OF ALL, WOULD YOU

00:14:10.901 --> 00:14:11.569
PLEASE LET ME SEE OUR DEAR

00:14:11.569 --> 00:14:12.538
PRINCESS NIA?

00:14:12.538 --> 00:14:14.174
I NEED TO KNOW SHE’S SAFE.

00:14:14.174 --> 00:14:15.878
I WOULD LIKE TO THANK HER FOR

00:14:15.878 --> 00:14:16.913
BEING KIND TO ME.

00:14:16.913 --> 00:14:17.915
&gt;&gt; Kittan: SHE’S GOT NERVE,

00:14:17.915 --> 00:14:19.217
COMING HERE ALONE LIKE THAT!

00:14:19.217 --> 00:14:20.621
I’M GONNA DECK HER!

00:14:20.621 --> 00:14:21.556
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: DON’T FORGET.

00:14:21.556 --> 00:14:22.558
DAI‐GURREN STILL ISN’T READY

00:14:22.558 --> 00:14:23.392
YET.

00:14:23.392 --> 00:14:24.294
WE MIGHT NEED TO FIND A WAY TO

00:14:24.294 --> 00:14:25.898
BUY SOME TIME.

00:14:25.898 --> 00:14:26.533
&gt;&gt; Kittan: GOOD POINT.

00:14:26.533 --> 00:14:27.902
OKAY, LET’S HAND OVER THE GIRL.

00:14:27.902 --> 00:14:29.204
&gt;&gt; Simon: NO!

00:14:29.204 --> 00:14:30.941
&gt;&gt; Kittan: WHAT’D YOU JUST SAY?!

00:14:30.941 --> 00:14:32.077
YOU GOT A PROBLEM WITH THE

00:14:32.077 --> 00:14:33.079
DECISIONS MADE BY YOUR MIGHTY

00:14:33.079 --> 00:14:34.147
LEADER, HUH, DO YA, DO YA?

00:14:34.147 --> 00:14:35.383
&gt;&gt; Simon: I’M NOT SURE WHY, BUT

00:14:35.383 --> 00:14:37.320
SOMETHING TELLS ME THAT’D BE

00:14:37.320 --> 00:14:37.888
RISKY.

00:14:37.888 --> 00:14:38.523
&gt;&gt; Kittan: DON’T GIVE ME THAT

00:14:38.523 --> 00:14:39.257
HALF‐ASSED CRAP!

00:14:39.257 --> 00:14:40.527
COME OUT AND SAY IT!

00:14:40.527 --> 00:14:41.428
QUIT YAMMERING...

00:14:41.428 --> 00:14:42.531
&gt;&gt; Nia: IT’S FINE.

00:14:42.531 --> 00:14:45.504
I WILL GO TO HER.

00:14:45.504 --> 00:14:46.539
&gt;&gt; Kittan: HEAR THAT?

00:14:46.539 --> 00:14:47.541
SHE SAYS SHE’S OKAY WITH IT!

00:14:47.541 --> 00:14:48.543
SO LET’S JUST TURN HER OVER AND

00:14:48.543 --> 00:14:49.144
BE DONE WITH IT!

00:14:49.144 --> 00:14:50.547
&gt;&gt; Simon: YEAH, BUT...

00:14:50.547 --> 00:14:51.883
&gt;&gt; Yoko: DON’T WORRY, YOU GUYS.

00:14:51.883 --> 00:14:53.052
I HAVE A FEELING THAT NIA HERE

00:14:53.052 --> 00:14:55.056
MIGHT ACTUALLY BE ABLE TO AVOID

00:14:55.056 --> 00:14:56.258
A BATTLE.

00:14:56.258 --> 00:14:57.561
&gt;&gt; Nia: MISS YOKO, THANK YOU FOR

00:14:57.561 --> 00:14:58.997
ALLOWING ME TO DO THIS.

00:14:58.997 --> 00:14:59.565
&gt;&gt; Yoko: DON’T GET

00:14:59.565 --> 00:15:00.466
THE WRONG IDEA.

00:15:00.466 --> 00:15:01.468
THIS DOESN’T MEAN THAT I

00:15:01.468 --> 00:15:02.337
TRUST YOU.

00:15:02.337 --> 00:15:03.372
I’M GONNA HAVE THIS RIFLE

00:15:03.372 --> 00:15:04.542
TRAINED ON YOUR BACK

00:15:04.542 --> 00:15:05.878
THE ENTIRE TIME.

00:15:05.878 --> 00:15:07.247
IF I SEE ANY FUNNY BUSINESS,

00:15:07.247 --> 00:15:09.619
I WON’T HESITATE.

00:15:09.619 --> 00:15:11.623
&gt;&gt; Nia: RIGHT.

00:15:11.623 --> 00:15:13.125
&gt;&gt; I’M GLAD YOU’RE SAFE,

00:15:13.125 --> 00:15:14.595
PRINCESS NIA.

00:15:14.595 --> 00:15:16.966
&gt;&gt; Nia: TELL ME, ADIANE.

00:15:16.966 --> 00:15:18.235
ARE YOU AND THE OTHERS FIGHTING

00:15:18.235 --> 00:15:19.605
THE HUMANS ON THE SURFACE AND

00:15:19.605 --> 00:15:22.110
TRYING TO MAKE THEM SUFFER?

00:15:25.684 --> 00:15:27.153
&gt;&gt; IT’S AS YOU SAY, PRINCESS.

00:15:27.153 --> 00:15:29.090
OUR DUTY IS TO SEEK OUT EVERY

00:15:29.090 --> 00:15:30.326
LAST HUMAN ON THE SURFACE

00:15:30.326 --> 00:15:31.696
AND TO SLAUGHTER EVERY ONE.

00:15:31.696 --> 00:15:33.332
&gt;&gt; Nia: AND TELL ME, WAS IT MY

00:15:33.332 --> 00:15:34.535
FATHER WHO ORDERED YOU TO CARRY

00:15:34.535 --> 00:15:35.403
OUT THESE ACTIONS?

00:15:35.403 --> 00:15:36.405
&gt;&gt; YES.

00:15:36.405 --> 00:15:37.942
&gt;&gt; Nia: AND UPON RECEIVING THESE

00:15:37.942 --> 00:15:39.177
ORDERS FROM MY FATHER, YOU

00:15:39.177 --> 00:15:40.647
HARBORED NO DOUBTS ABOUT THEM?

00:15:40.647 --> 00:15:42.518
&gt;&gt; DID I "DOUBT" THEM? NEVER!

00:15:42.518 --> 00:15:45.223
HUMANS ARE AS LOWLY AS WORMS,

00:15:45.223 --> 00:15:46.458
MAYBE EVEN LOWLIER.

00:15:46.458 --> 00:15:47.962
THEIR SUFFERING AND THEIR

00:15:47.962 --> 00:15:49.231
PITIFUL LITTLE DEATHS ARE

00:15:49.231 --> 00:15:50.266
BENEATH OUR NOTICE,

00:15:50.266 --> 00:15:50.701
PRINCESS NIA.

00:15:50.701 --> 00:15:51.636
&gt;&gt; Kittan: AS LOWLY AS WORMS.

00:15:51.636 --> 00:15:53.005
&gt;&gt; Nia: I CANNOT BELIEVE THIS!

00:15:53.005 --> 00:15:54.942
I WANT TO DISCUSS THIS WITH MY

00:15:54.942 --> 00:15:55.376
FATHER!

00:15:55.376 --> 00:15:56.078
ADIANE, THE ELEGANT,

00:15:56.078 --> 00:15:57.648
IN THE NAME OF THE SPIRAL KING,

00:15:57.648 --> 00:15:59.552
I ORDER YOU TO TAKE ME TO HIM!

00:15:59.552 --> 00:16:01.121
&gt;&gt; YOU REALLY PISS ME OFF!

00:16:01.121 --> 00:16:02.157
IF YOU WANNA GO, TAKE YOUR OWN

00:16:02.157 --> 00:16:04.060
SORRY ASS!

00:16:04.060 --> 00:16:05.964
&gt;&gt; Nia: WHAT DID YOU SAY?

00:16:05.964 --> 00:16:08.068
&gt;&gt; HAS IT NOT SUNK IN YET,

00:16:08.068 --> 00:16:09.404
YOU, LITTLE DARLING, AREN’T A

00:16:09.404 --> 00:16:10.306
PRINCESS ANYMORE!

00:16:10.306 --> 00:16:12.578
THE SPIRAL KING HAS ABANDONED,

00:16:12.578 --> 00:16:15.116
ABANDONED, ABANDONED YOU!

00:16:15.116 --> 00:16:16.553
I DON’T KNOW WHAT YOU DID,

00:16:16.553 --> 00:16:18.155
BUT HE SAID I SHOULD KILL YOU

00:16:18.155 --> 00:16:19.324
WITH THE REST OF THE WORMS!

00:16:19.324 --> 00:16:20.727
&gt;&gt; Nia: HE ABANDONED ME?

00:16:20.727 --> 00:16:22.063
KILL ME?

00:16:22.063 --> 00:16:23.533
HE REALLY SAID YOU SHOULD

00:16:23.533 --> 00:16:24.301
KILL ME?

00:16:24.301 --> 00:16:26.606
&gt;&gt; Simon: SHE WAS ABANDONED?

00:16:31.381 --> 00:16:33.152
LAGANN!

00:16:33.152 --> 00:16:34.287
COME ON.

00:16:34.287 --> 00:16:35.156
PLEASE JUST WORK.

00:16:35.156 --> 00:16:36.124
I WAS RIGHT!

00:16:36.124 --> 00:16:37.393
THAT WOMAN DID NOT COME HERE TO

00:16:37.393 --> 00:16:38.730
TAKE NIA BACK!

00:16:38.730 --> 00:16:39.665
&gt;&gt; Nia: YOU’RE LYING!

00:16:39.665 --> 00:16:41.034
IT CAN’T BE‐‐ FATHER WOULD NEVER

00:16:41.034 --> 00:16:42.270
DO SUCH A HORRIBLE THING.

00:16:42.270 --> 00:16:43.607
&gt;&gt; OH, HE WOULDN’T?

00:16:43.607 --> 00:16:44.642
YOU JUST THINK WHATEVER YOU

00:16:44.642 --> 00:16:45.409
WANT!

00:16:45.409 --> 00:16:47.180
EITHER WAY, I’M SENDING YOU OFF

00:16:47.180 --> 00:16:49.184
TO THE NEXT WORLD, MISSY!

00:16:49.184 --> 00:16:50.554
&gt;&gt; Nia: SO DOES THIS MEAN

00:16:50.554 --> 00:16:51.589
YOU HATE ME TOO, ADIANE?

00:16:51.589 --> 00:16:53.192
&gt;&gt; HATE YOU?

00:16:53.192 --> 00:16:54.294
I REALLY COULDN’T CARE LESS

00:16:54.294 --> 00:16:57.267
ABOUT YOU.

00:16:57.267 --> 00:16:59.371
I WAS TOLD TO KILL YOU,

00:16:59.371 --> 00:17:01.141
SO THAT’S PRECISELY WHAT I’M

00:17:01.141 --> 00:17:02.443
GOING TO DO!

00:17:02.443 --> 00:17:04.247
WHETHER OR NOT I HATE YOU

00:17:04.247 --> 00:17:05.617
IS IRRELEVANT!

00:17:05.617 --> 00:17:07.053
&gt;&gt; Nia: SO YOU’RE SAYING THAT

00:17:07.053 --> 00:17:08.055
YOU’RE WILLING KILL ME...

00:17:08.055 --> 00:17:09.559
SIMPLY BECAUSE YOU WERE ORDERED

00:17:09.559 --> 00:17:10.727
TO DO SO?

00:17:10.727 --> 00:17:11.729
&gt;&gt; OF COURSE I AM!

00:17:11.729 --> 00:17:12.497
WHAT OF IT?!

00:17:12.497 --> 00:17:13.733
&gt;&gt; Nia: IF MY FATHER ORDERED YOU

00:17:13.733 --> 00:17:15.102
TO TAKE YOUR OWN LIFE, WOULD YOU

00:17:15.102 --> 00:17:18.710
DO THAT, TOO?

00:17:18.710 --> 00:17:19.712
YOU HAVE GOT THIS ALL WRONG,

00:17:19.712 --> 00:17:21.081
ADIANE!

00:17:21.081 --> 00:17:22.417
THESE PEOPLE ARE DECENT AND

00:17:22.417 --> 00:17:24.120
GOOD, AND THEY HAVE DONE NOTHING

00:17:24.120 --> 00:17:24.589
WRONG!

00:17:24.589 --> 00:17:26.358
THEIR ONLY WISH IS TO LIVE

00:17:26.358 --> 00:17:27.695
ON THE SURFACE IN PEACE!

00:17:27.695 --> 00:17:29.231
IT CANNOT BE RIGHT TO KILL THEM

00:17:29.231 --> 00:17:30.701
FOR NO REASON.

00:17:30.701 --> 00:17:33.172
&gt;&gt; THESE PEOPLE KILLED THYMILPH.

00:17:33.172 --> 00:17:34.241
&gt;&gt; Nia: THEY DID?

00:17:34.241 --> 00:17:35.711
&gt;&gt; THAT SHOULD BE REASON ENOUGH

00:17:35.711 --> 00:17:37.146
TO END THEIR LIVES!

00:17:37.146 --> 00:17:39.719
&gt;&gt; Nia: NO. NO, YOU’RE WRONG.

00:17:39.719 --> 00:17:41.589
THAT ISN’T RIGHT.

00:17:41.589 --> 00:17:43.125
THEY THEMSELVES HAVE LOST A MAN

00:17:43.125 --> 00:17:43.727
THEY CALL BRO.

00:17:43.727 --> 00:17:46.265
THIS LOSS HAS LEFT THEM SORELY

00:17:46.265 --> 00:17:46.733
WOUNDED.

00:17:46.733 --> 00:17:50.039
YES, THAT IS WHAT HAPPENS WHEN

00:17:50.039 --> 00:17:51.208
SOMEONE DIES.

00:17:51.208 --> 00:17:52.544
PEOPLE SUFFER.

00:17:52.544 --> 00:17:54.682
AND YET HERE YOU ARE, SAYING TWO

00:17:54.682 --> 00:17:56.318
GRIEVING PARTIES SHOULD HURT

00:17:56.318 --> 00:17:57.253
EACH OTHER!

00:17:57.253 --> 00:17:58.757
DON’T YOU THINK THERE MIGHT BE

00:17:58.757 --> 00:17:59.692
SOMETHING WRONG WITH THAT?

00:17:59.692 --> 00:18:01.328
&gt;&gt; NO, I DON’T, BECAUSE THERE

00:18:01.328 --> 00:18:02.765
ISN’T!

00:18:02.765 --> 00:18:04.167
&gt;&gt; Simon: FINE!

00:18:04.167 --> 00:18:06.706
PIECE OF CRAP!

00:18:06.706 --> 00:18:09.177
NIA!

00:18:11.281 --> 00:18:12.551
&gt;&gt; YOU REALLY KNOW HOW TO PISS

00:18:12.551 --> 00:18:13.419
PEOPLE OFF!

00:18:13.419 --> 00:18:14.789
I UNDERSTAND WHY THE SPIRAL KING

00:18:14.789 --> 00:18:16.224
WAS SO EAGER TO GET RID OF YOU!

00:18:16.224 --> 00:18:17.360
&gt;&gt; Nia: NOW I SEE!

00:18:17.360 --> 00:18:19.497
YOU ARE A PISSING‐OFF PERSON!

00:18:19.497 --> 00:18:20.667
&gt;&gt; HEY, BE QUIET!

00:18:20.667 --> 00:18:22.136
THAT’S MY LINE, MISSY!

00:18:22.136 --> 00:18:23.205
&gt;&gt; Simon: NIA!

00:18:23.205 --> 00:18:24.441
&gt;&gt; Nia: SIMON!

00:18:24.441 --> 00:18:25.409
SIMON!

00:18:25.409 --> 00:18:28.282
&gt;&gt; Simon: NIA!

00:18:30.186 --> 00:18:31.455
&gt;&gt; Kittan: THIS SPIRAL KING

00:18:31.455 --> 00:18:32.357
THREW OUT HIS OWN DAUGHTER?!

00:18:32.357 --> 00:18:34.260
THAT’S ONE THING I WON’T STAND

00:18:34.260 --> 00:18:35.129
FOR!

00:18:35.129 --> 00:18:36.699
&gt;&gt; WE WON’T STAND FOR IT!

00:18:36.699 --> 00:18:38.536
&gt;&gt; DIE!

00:18:40.473 --> 00:18:43.112
&gt;&gt; Yoko: GO FOR IT, GUYS!

00:19:03.352 --> 00:19:05.222
&gt;&gt; STINKING HUMANS!

00:19:15.711 --> 00:19:17.313
&gt;&gt; Kittan: ZORTHY!

00:19:17.313 --> 00:19:19.150
YOU BITCH!

00:19:19.150 --> 00:19:20.721
&gt;&gt; COME ON, YOU THIRD‐RATE

00:19:20.721 --> 00:19:21.522
GUNMEN!

00:19:21.522 --> 00:19:22.691
COME RIGHT AT ME, EVERYBODY AT

00:19:22.691 --> 00:19:23.927
ONCE!

00:19:23.927 --> 00:19:26.264
SO THAT I CAN TEAR EACH ONE

00:19:26.264 --> 00:19:26.666
OF YOU APART.

00:19:26.666 --> 00:19:28.235
&gt;&gt; COME ON!

00:19:28.235 --> 00:19:29.404
ISN’T THIS THING WORKING YET?!

00:19:29.404 --> 00:19:31.174
&gt;&gt; Ron: I’M TRYING!

00:19:31.174 --> 00:19:33.813
OKAY, HOW ABOUT NOW?

00:19:44.535 --> 00:19:46.371
&gt;&gt; Adiane: WHAT?!

00:19:54.421 --> 00:19:55.657
IMPOSSIBLE.

00:19:55.657 --> 00:19:56.491
IT BROKE MY SPINE!

00:19:56.491 --> 00:19:57.928
&gt;&gt; WE GOT HER!

00:19:57.928 --> 00:19:59.431
&gt;&gt; YEAH, GOT HER!

00:19:59.431 --> 00:20:00.567
&gt;&gt; Kittan: NOW SQUASH HER!

00:20:00.567 --> 00:20:01.669
&gt;&gt; Ron: OH, WE’D LIKE TO,

00:20:01.669 --> 00:20:03.372
BELIEVE ME, BUT WE CAN’T EXACTLY

00:20:03.372 --> 00:20:03.940
SEE WHERE WE’RE AIMING!

00:20:03.940 --> 00:20:05.209
&gt;&gt; NUMBER THREE BRIDGE!

00:20:05.209 --> 00:20:06.411
&gt;&gt; YOU GOT HER!

00:20:06.411 --> 00:20:07.346
YOU GOT HER, HURRY!

00:20:07.346 --> 00:20:08.817
&gt;&gt; THAT’S IT! THAT’S THE WAY!

00:20:08.817 --> 00:20:12.490
&gt;&gt; LOOK OUT UP AHEAD!

00:20:12.490 --> 00:20:13.392
&gt;&gt; Ron: WHAT WAS THAT?

00:20:13.392 --> 00:20:16.398
WHAT JUST HAPPENED?

00:20:16.398 --> 00:20:17.735
&gt;&gt; IT’S ENKIDU.

00:20:17.735 --> 00:20:18.770
VIRAL, IS THAT YOU?

00:20:18.770 --> 00:20:19.705
&gt;&gt; I HOPE YOU’LL FORGIVE ME FOR

00:20:19.705 --> 00:20:21.374
DISOBEYING ORDERS, MA’AM.

00:20:21.374 --> 00:20:23.245
IT’S JUST THAT I HAVE MY OWN

00:20:23.245 --> 00:20:24.447
HONOR I MUST UPHOLD!

00:20:31.394 --> 00:20:32.296
&gt;&gt; GO AWAY!

00:20:32.296 --> 00:20:33.600
I WON’T WITHDRAW FROM A BATTLE

00:20:33.600 --> 00:20:33.967
LIKE THIS!

00:20:33.967 --> 00:20:35.269
&gt;&gt; YOU CAN KEEP ON FIGHTING AS

00:20:35.269 --> 00:20:36.371
LONG AS YOU’RE ALIVE.

00:20:36.371 --> 00:20:37.941
BUT WE’RE GOING TO EXECUTE

00:20:37.941 --> 00:20:40.547
A STRATEGIC RETREAT.

00:20:40.547 --> 00:20:42.551
YOU!

00:20:42.551 --> 00:20:44.421
WE’RE RETREATING FOR NOW,

00:20:44.421 --> 00:20:45.891
BUT WHEN NEXT WE MEET,

00:20:45.891 --> 00:20:46.893
WE’LL SETTLE MATTERS ONCE AND

00:20:46.893 --> 00:20:48.362
FOR ALL!

00:20:48.362 --> 00:20:52.303
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: WHAT’S HE MEAN?

00:20:52.303 --> 00:20:53.606
&gt;&gt; Kittan: THEY’RE GONE!

00:20:53.606 --> 00:20:53.973
THEY BUGGED OUT!

00:20:53.973 --> 00:20:55.309
&gt;&gt; WE DID IT!

00:20:55.309 --> 00:20:56.612
WE DROVE THEM OFF!

00:20:56.612 --> 00:20:58.248
&gt;&gt; Ron: OH, GOODNESS GRACIOUS.

00:20:58.248 --> 00:20:59.919
ALL THIS STRESS IS MURDER

00:20:59.919 --> 00:21:00.554
ON MY SKIN.

00:21:00.554 --> 00:21:01.556
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: HEY, ARE YOU OKAY

00:21:01.556 --> 00:21:02.558
THERE, NIA?

00:21:02.558 --> 00:21:04.528
&gt;&gt; Nia: YES. THANK YOU.

00:21:04.528 --> 00:21:06.699
BUT I MUST APOLOGIZE.

00:21:06.699 --> 00:21:08.302
I PUT YOU ALL IN DANGER.

00:21:08.302 --> 00:21:09.437
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: THERE’S NOTHING FOR

00:21:09.437 --> 00:21:10.439
YOU TO BE SORRY ABOUT.

00:21:10.439 --> 00:21:13.680
JUST TAKE A LOOK BEHIND YOU.

00:21:13.680 --> 00:21:15.449
[cheering]

00:21:15.449 --> 00:21:17.988
&gt;&gt; NIA, YEAH!

00:21:20.392 --> 00:21:22.664
&gt;&gt; Kittan: NIA!

00:21:23.633 --> 00:21:25.369
&gt;&gt; NIA!

00:21:25.369 --> 00:21:26.739
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: THEY’RE ALL HAPPY TO

00:21:26.739 --> 00:21:29.310
SEE YOU SAFE AND SOUND.

00:21:29.310 --> 00:21:30.881
&gt;&gt; Nia: THANK YOU, EVERYBODY.

00:21:30.881 --> 00:21:31.949
THANK YOU. THANK YOU, ALL!

00:21:31.949 --> 00:21:35.624
[cheering continues]

00:21:38.328 --> 00:21:41.334
&gt;&gt; YOU SCUM! TRASH! VERMIN!

00:21:41.334 --> 00:21:42.370
WHAT’S THE BIG IDEA,

00:21:42.370 --> 00:21:44.407
LEAVING WITHOUT A VICTORY?

00:21:44.407 --> 00:21:45.811
I CAN’T RETURN TO THE CAPITAL,

00:21:45.811 --> 00:21:46.846
NOT BEFORE I’VE GOTTEN

00:21:46.846 --> 00:21:48.415
MY REVENGE.

00:21:48.415 --> 00:21:49.618
WHO DO YOU THINK I AM,

00:21:49.618 --> 00:21:52.423
YOU WORTHLESS, ROTTEN, IDIOT!

00:21:52.423 --> 00:21:55.630
[punching continues]

00:21:55.630 --> 00:21:56.699
&gt;&gt; Nia: WELL MET, MY GOOD

00:21:56.699 --> 00:21:59.538
PIG‐MOLE.

00:21:59.538 --> 00:22:02.009
IS SIMON INSIDE?

00:22:02.009 --> 00:22:04.582
SIMON? SIMON?

00:22:04.582 --> 00:22:06.051
ARE YOU IN THERE?

00:22:06.051 --> 00:22:07.821
I BROUGHT YOU SOME DINNER.

00:22:07.821 --> 00:22:11.494
[knocking]

00:22:11.494 --> 00:22:13.800
SIMON, EVERYBODY KEEPS TELLING

00:22:13.800 --> 00:22:15.537
ME HOW HAPPY THEY ARE TO SEE ME

00:22:15.537 --> 00:22:17.306
SAFE AND SOUND, EVEN THOUGH I’M

00:22:17.306 --> 00:22:18.576
THE DAUGHTER OF THEIR ENEMY.

00:22:18.576 --> 00:22:20.012
IT’S JUST AS I FIRST THOUGHT.

00:22:20.012 --> 00:22:21.481
THE PEOPLE HERE ARE VERY KIND.

00:22:21.481 --> 00:22:24.053
BUT I KNOW.

00:22:24.053 --> 00:22:25.322
I KNOW THAT YOU WERE THE FIRST

00:22:25.322 --> 00:22:27.628
ONE TO RUN TO MY RESCUE, SIMON.

00:22:27.628 --> 00:22:29.364
AND THAT WAS VERY BRAVE

00:22:29.364 --> 00:22:31.468
AND KIND.

00:22:31.468 --> 00:22:35.009
AND SO I THANK YOU.

00:22:37.013 --> 00:22:38.616
&gt;&gt; Simon: I CAN’T DO IT.

00:22:38.616 --> 00:22:40.520
I’LL NEVER BE ABLE TO BE LIKE

00:22:40.520 --> 00:22:42.624
YOU, BRO.

