&gt;&gt; Nia: INSIDE A PERSON’S HEART,

00:24:19.718 --> 00:24:21.054
THERE IS A DEEP, DARK,

00:24:21.054 --> 00:24:22.858
FRIGHTENING HOLE.

00:24:22.858 --> 00:24:24.828
EVENTUALLY, THIS HOLE BECOMES

00:24:24.828 --> 00:24:26.197
A NEW TUNNEL.

